title: Should Nick Cannon Be Neutered?! He's Got A Tenth Kid On The Way
description:
Congratulations are in order for Nick Cannon… again!
He and model Brittany Bell are having a baby, making this his tenth child altogether but his third with Brittany. They have a 5-year-old son Golden Sagon and a 19-month-old daughter named Powerful Queen.
